‘Human Harvest: China’s Organ Trafficking’ will show how human rights lawyer David Matas and former Canadian member of parliament David Kilgour investigated allegations of organ harvesting of Falun Gong practitioners in China . 
  It is claimed the illegal organ trade is now worth a staggering US$1 billion a year . 
  10,000 organs are transplanted in China every year but only a tiny number of people are on the official donor register . 
  It's claimed political prisoners are being used as live organ donors . 
 